I'd like to add that i'm also experiencing the same issue (using NVIDIA Blob & Ubuntu 18.10/GNOME 3.30 + XOrg). Was curious about something....the patch hard-codes to a specific refresh rate. Would it not be possible/better advised for a dynamic approach, where the compositor identifies the currently selected/used monitor refresh rate and uses that value for the compositor refresh rate?

@vanvugt / @jpleau , would either of you mind informing me how to apply the patch so I can participate in giving feedback? :)

